long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The StratoQ Chrome Extension lets you submit print jobs directly to your organization's worldwide My Prints queue, right from Chrome.  Print jobs are then made available for release at any of your copiers/MFDs.

After installation, you'll be asked to authenticate using your work or school account so we know which user and company your print jobs belong to.  After that, any time you're signed in and use the "print" function in chrome you'll have a new "StratoQ" printer available...simple as that!
